      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;I’m Nobody! Who are you? Are you – Nobody – too? Then there’s a pair of us!&lt;/em&gt; ~ Emily Dickinson&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hello, stranger!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My name is Boudhayan Bhattacharya but you may better know me by my online
alias &lt;em&gt;bbhtt&lt;/em&gt;. I live in India and I&amp;rsquo;m currently doing Ph.D. in
Mathematics. I teach for a living and I sometimes &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/bbhtt&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;contribute&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href=&#34;https://gitlab.com/bbhtt&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;to&lt;/a&gt; various &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Free_and_open-source_software&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;FOSS&lt;/a&gt;
projects during my free time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I like watching &lt;a href=&#34;https://letterboxd.com/bbhtt/films/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;movies&lt;/a&gt;, TV shows
and &lt;a href=&#34;https://anidb.net/user/983003&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;anime&lt;/a&gt;; reading books and listening
to &lt;a href=&#34;https://open.spotify.com/user/m18qz71984e1gjbkfbd36zwmi&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;music and podcasts&lt;/a&gt;.
I play casual online chess sometimes, although I never studied it
seriously. I&amp;rsquo;m also heavily addicted to YouTube. I have an account on
&lt;a href=&#34;https://x.com/bbhtt_&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.reddit.com/user/bbhtt/&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;Reddit&lt;/a&gt;
too but I&amp;rsquo;m mostly inactive there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a place for random things in life that I find interesting.&lt;/p&gt;
